{"tid":479323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(大導演) 王家衛招募男女演員, 要作「裸露」和操流利廣東話","createTime":"2017-11-25T04:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-25T11:08:36.000Z","uid":134071,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"414132bb06a780902f5200c73822db8b6fff7b77","tid":479323,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:11:53.000Z","msg":"王家衛執導的美國劇集《Tong Wars》現正為四位角色招募演員, 所有角色也要懂得說流利廣東話及美式英語.  其中有兩個角色(一男一女)更要求演員作一些「裸露」和床上戲演出.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155333689482979&amp;set=gm.10154973084566767&amp;type=3&amp;permPage=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10155333689482979%26set%3Dgm.10154973084566767%26type%3D3%26permPage%3D1&d=WgNO9hVBjMQuj%2F7zOV%2BdGaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=b3cb3d50\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10155333689482979&amp;set=gm.10154973084566767&amp;type=3&amp;permPage=1</a><br />\n<br />\nTALENT SEARCH -CANADA &amp; ASIA. Renowned director Wong Kar-Wai's American TV series. English+Cantonese bilingual actors &amp; new faces needed. Please share. Email PoPing at tongwarspopingcasting@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/25/121118_6961cbd616157f51f885c8ba7eb8239c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F25%2F121118_6961cbd616157f51f885c8ba7eb8239c.jpg&h=0ca13c58&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"866eb8bde7938dbab808308941e22e9e223b8abf","tid":479323,"uid":34562,"like":57,"dislike":0,"score":57,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:21:19.000Z","msg":"唔直接搵湯唯？"},{"pid":"90dab2c71821151d4e182d7e1710326bd97d7145","tid":479323,"uid":134071,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-25T04:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔直接搵湯唯？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能一早搵左  <br />\n<br />\n(留意 - 女主角的後生版演員, 並不包括在此公開招募.  而女主角在後生時是一位妓女.)"},{"pid":"8ced1c63ee498c86a1051a4fba5